            In the <emphasis effect="italics">z</emphasis>-domain we find that
            <equation id="id331892">
              <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
                <m:mtable displaystyle="true">
                  <m:mtr>
                    <m:mtd columnalign="right">
                      <m:mrow>
